    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as-is. While it remains functional for daily commuting, it shows noticeable signs of wear both inside and out, including some minor exterior dents and upholstery thinning. The engine runs but would benefit from a comprehensive tune-up, and the suspension is beginning to feel loose on uneven roads. This is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who is willing to invest a little bit of work into long-term maintenance.",
